snippet: People seeking to get or stay fit in 2015 might do better to start today rather than rely on a New Year’s resolution to shape up tomorrow, fitness experts say....

headline.print_headline: New Year’s Resolutions May Be More Procrastination Than Motivation
headline.main: New Year’s Resolutions May Be More Procrastination Than Motivation

lead_paragraph: People seeking to get or stay fit in 2015 might do better to start today rather than rely on a New Year’s resolution to shape up tomorrow, fitness experts say.
